    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256380/extras/1ae4da0e92bed99826b4d1a0a296e342.poster.avif?t=1696983329\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256380/extras/1ae4da0e92bed99826b4d1a0a296e342.webm?t=1696983329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256380/extras/1ae4da0e92bed99826b4d1a0a296e342.mp4?t=1696983329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【独立生存模式】来自原游戏《妖谈：百妖夜行》</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事</h2>你无意中打破了你家储藏间那本神秘书的封印。这本神话书有一股巨大的魔力，辅助使用者可以打败任何妖怪，并记录下他们的名字，从而控制他们。这种神圣的力量太强大了，惊动了所有附近的妖怪。在他们攻打过来时，你必须找到自己的方法去战胜他们取得胜利。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Roguelike塔防</h2>欢迎来到一个引人入胜的游戏体验！在基于象棋的战场上，战略地部署单位，保卫领土，同时通过升级获得Roguelike风格的超过30种独特的装备，带来令人兴奋的定制化。每场战斗都提供多样的策略和体验，确保无尽的刺激和可玩性。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256380/extras/e6f0ee448f9640b73af2205e6ac91478.poster.avif?t=1696983329\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256380/extras/e6f0ee448f9640b73af2205e6ac91478.webm?t=1696983329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256380/extras/e6f0ee448f9640b73af2205e6ac91478.mp4?t=1696983329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >单位与技能</h2>释放15个主战和辅助单位的力量，每个单位都有独特的专长和多样的设计。从高输出的伤害输出者到坚韧的坦克、治疗者、增益者和控制效果专家，组建一支强大的团队。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256380/extras/eff55bf5b9d437989c169d31f348b836.poster.avif?t=1696983329\" width=596 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256380/extras/eff55bf5b9d437989c169d31f348b836.webm?t=1696983329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256380/extras/eff55bf5b9d437989c169d31f348b836.mp4?t=1696983329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>将你的单位进化到最终形态，发挥出他们真正的潜力。利用力量石释放他们独一无二的毁灭性强大技能。准备好通过战略性升级和布阵在战场上称霸吧。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256380/extras/8da8d397b3ff259f3dcd045e48e9610c.poster.avif?t=1696983329\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256380/extras/8da8d397b3ff259f3dcd045e48e9610c.webm?t=1696983329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256380/extras/8da8d397b3ff259f3dcd045e48e9610c.mp4?t=1696983329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256380/extras/099a9fda6e767af2d330d94a9c60477b.poster.avif?t=1696983329\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256380/extras/099a9fda6e767af2d330d94a9c60477b.webm?t=1696983329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256380/extras/099a9fda6e767af2d330d94a9c60477b.mp4?t=1696983329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Boss挑战</h2>迎击各种小Boss，展现你的策略技巧，并面对终极挑战：骷髅王。坚持到最后一刻，在这个扣人心弦的冒险中获得胜利。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256380/extras/2962ac5e882831f40b656d531a292c64.poster.avif?t=1696983329\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256380/extras/2962ac5e882831f40b656d531a292c64.webm?t=1696983329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256380/extras/2962ac5e882831f40b656d531a292c64.mp4?t=1696983329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
